title: Thursday Post Show (02-24-22)
itunes:title: Thursday Post Show (02-24-22)
description:
Bobby begins by reading some love/hate emails we got sent into the mailbag. Bobby shares what criteria he has now for celebrity interviews. Bobby also shares how the FBI has acknowledged a UFO sighting of last year. Lunchbox shares while the Girl Scouts are ripping people off. Amy also shares a story about getting a strange picture from a guy who was supposed to come to her house to work on something…and she couldn't believe it.
